        <div class="instructions">
            <p><strong>Instructions</strong></p>
            <p>Enter the latitude and longitude of three points on Earth. The calculator will compute:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>The distance between the first two points (in meters)</li>
                <li>The angle formed by the three points (in degrees)</li>
                <li>The area of the triangle formed by the three points (in square meters)</li>
                <li>The angle between the first two points and North (in degrees)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

